"pid":"ee849847dae482ce78a71a66263261ed1ad7e3eb","tid":2488704,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"識一個6年 當然中間有斷斷續續 但係最後得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfacdb299e6d50988dfa59daeb204e08b5928ca","tid":2488704,"uid":79126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"睇你有冇比反應佢"},{"pid":"93281f2cd8ce7f269b1e30d4877eac29f4fb1c5d","tid":2488704,"uid":393145,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fbf7dea2eab4c0aa8f7b57ab8dcf511df580dce4","tid":2488704,"uid":393145,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"真係真係真係好中意<br />\n相信有啲人其實幾耐都願意<br />\n能夠追到咁耐keep住聯絡<br />\n其實雙方本身都有一定感情關係<br />\n而唔係有人要特登拖特登玩嘢試探<br />\n確實有人係好耐至對人有信心肯交託<br />\n確實有人係唔介意追咁耐<br />\n身邊都聽過呢啲故仔<br />\n<br />\n只要你唔好呃住人<br />\n明明拍住拖又扮單身 <br />\n又一路呻冇人珍惜你<br />\n呻冇信心拍拖唔敢拍拖<br />\n<br />\n追一個單身既人好耐都可以<br />\n等一個拍拖既人好耐都可以 <br />\n知道咩事唔會做乜 等就OK<br />\n有人係可以等人好耐<br />\n<br />\n但纏一個扮單身而實際拍緊拖好耐既人<br />\n就唔可以<br />\n你過到你嗰關 我過唔到 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"身邊有個男仔<br />\n由初中追個女仔追到大學<br />\n因為個女仔屋企唔俾拍拖<br />\n個男仔好認真好真心追<br />\n但唔係狗公嗰種<br />\n係真係陪伴 真係默默守護<br />\n一齊讀書 互相扶持 了解<br />\n個女仔亦真係冇拍過拖<br />\n個女仔因為背景問題<br />\n係好難對人對感情有信心<br />\n叫過個男仔好多次唔好等唔好追<br />\n佢真係唔想拍拖 冇信心拍拖<br />\n但個男仔一直陪 一直留<br />\n最後經歷咁多年<br />\n都知道個男仔係可託付既對象<br />\n去到大學其實屋企人都本身仲係唔俾拍拖<br />\n但連屋企人都為個男仔感動到<br />\n最終俾佢哋拍拖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而同時 另一個中學女仔朋友<br />\n中意咗個男仔幾年<br />\n個男仔一直都係話自己單身冇女<br />\n冇人珍惜 唔想拍拖之類 <br />\n個女仔好努力陪佢安慰佢支持佢<br />\n希望有日個男仔會對愛情有返信心<br />\n就算唔係同佢一齊都真係唔緊要<br />\n最緊要搵到幸福<br />\n望住陪住愛既人有幸福就得<br />\n<br />\n但原來個男仔<br />\n一直咁耐幾年嚟都係拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍咗幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個男仔女朋友嗰邊啲人仲要屌9個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女仔至知原來佢拍咗咁耐咁多次拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有嘢都係假<br />\n<br />\n結果個女仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f389004354c66447055e60a820f3fed0e8730698","tid":2488704,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"鍾意咪一齊，唔鍾意咪拒絕人囉，做乜拖咁耐？"},{"pid":"ef46bbab959fb5636addbe48fb2b149f7a7ec184","tid":2488704,"uid":21248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"睇你有幾配合嘅姐 <br />\n如果唔係長期令佢灰心又囉囉攣我諗半年都okay 嘅"},{"pid":"c1935faa6f346b1b38e37c2bfb2ac6d3f7a2a1f7","tid":2488704,"uid":140347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"8 個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2605b1879b0d2da173d5f129a5534eee6ace474a","tid":2488704,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"無上限<br />\n如果溝唔到第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f19b997eda26c9da047d48d9e0f956ae20ca06","tid":2488704,"uid":257125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"少於一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪哂9大家時間"},{"pid":"8e73ee62548f604c415891422f26a40379096eaa","tid":2488704,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc