/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有嘢都係假<br />\n<br />\n結果個女仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"唔係所有付出同等待都可以有回報 想知最後個女仔點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b59699f31713c47c2dbe8bc30f638233c100bb","tid":2488704,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"唔得咪next 等你老味咩<br />\n戇鳩"},{"pid":"0b562a90741a8fcdcbbb5b2737f3583d3e28d73e","tid":2488704,"uid":223987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"我通常幾日就嫌麻煩冇左件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e92b4e311ea06c11fd0e1e1c2f39719723a3602","tid":2488704,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fbcddca787b7203e4c953e8cd79746e66388d3","tid":2488704,"uid":20689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba6378fda7575c181c747f279b25d400729f7f0d","tid":2488704,"uid":379026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:51:35.000Z","msg":"係咪過咗呢個期限之後就會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"你話呢？ 唔通用一世時間等你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"識人等左一個女人三十幾年，等到佢老公過生，最後一齊，仲要做埋兩個廿幾歲的後父<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befd2f6172f4ea0ae793fa192d663dfa75d38090","tid":2488704,"uid":90316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93281f2cd8ce7f269b1e30d4877eac29f4fb1c5d","tid":2488704,"uid":393145,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fbf7dea2eab4c0aa8f7b57ab8dcf511df580dce4","tid":2488704,"uid":393145,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"真係真係真係好中意<br />\n相信有啲人其實幾耐都願意<br />\n能夠追到咁